episodes.title: The Tailgate:  Mike Houck Talks About Coordinating Sooner Coverage
episodes.description:
As always we kick off the Podcast with Boomer Bytes... all the latest news involving Sooner Athletics.
But a very special guest joins us this week as we sit down with Mike Houck.  Mike is now the Assistant AD/Strategic Communications for the OU Athletic Department.  His primary objective is coordinating all things football with the media.  The long time Basketball Sports Information Director and Radio analyst is now in his second season with football and gives us some perspective on the shift from basketball to football and what goes in to a typical game week.

If you aren't already make sure you follow Mike on Twitter @MHouckOU

Next week we sit down with Joe Castiglione.  Make sure to send your questions for Joe C to us @OUontheAir.

Boomer!
